tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE project_financial_data (
  project_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  total_budget DECIMAL(15, 2),
  expenses DECIMAL(15, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(255),
 budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
 start_date DATE,
 end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE expenses (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_id INT,
 amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
 description TEXT,
 expense_date DATE,
 FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(id)
);
CREATE TABLE projects (    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    project_name TEXT NOT NULL,    budget DECIMAL NOT NULL,    start_date DATE NOT NULL,    end_date DATE NOT NULL );
CREATE TABLE expenses (    expense_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    project_id INT NOT NULL,    expense_amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,    expense_date DATE NOT NULL,    expense_description TEXT );
CREATE TABLE cost_analysis (    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,    project_id INT NOT NULL,    analysis_date DATE NOT NULL,    total_expenses DECIMAL NOT NULL,    budget_remaining DECIMAL NOT NULL );

CREATE TABLE projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  budget DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE expenses (
  expense_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  expense_date DATE,
  description VARCHAR(255),
  amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE cost_analysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  analysis_date DATE,
  total_spent DECIMAL(10, 2),
  remaining_budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
  financial_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  transaction_date DATE,
  transaction_type VARCHAR(255),
  amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE expenses (
    expense_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id UUID REFERENCES projects(project_id),
    expense_category VARCHAR(50),
    expense_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    expense_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE cost_analysis (
    analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id UUID REFERENCES projects(project_id),
    analysis_date DATE,
    total_expenses DECIMAL(15, 2),
    total_budget DECIMAL(15, 2)
);
